Title: User can edit a ToDo
Description:
As a user
When I click "Edit" next to a ToDo
Then I should see a Edit ToDo form with the description of the ToDo pre-filled
And when I edit to ToDo description and click "Update ToDo"
Then I should see "ToDo updated"
And I should see the updated ToDo description in my ToDo list

Title: User can finish a ToDo
Description:
As a user
When I click "Complete" next to a ToDo
Then I should see "ToDo completed"
And I should not see that ToDo in my ToDo list anymore

Title: User are seeing other users ToDos
Description: Users are complaining that they are seeing ToDo items from other user's in their list. A user should only see ToDos that they created.
